-- Mexico to Fall Into ‘Total Mediocrity’ Without Reforms: Loser
-- B y   D a v i d   P a p a d o p o u l o s
-- 2013-07-10T16:07:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-10/mexico-to-fall-into-total-mediocrity-without-reforms-loser.html
Mexico  needs to implement economic
reforms or it will slide into “total mediocrity,” Claudio
Loser, founder of Centennial Group, says at Bloomberg Mexico
Conference in New York.
*Mexico has been “very mediocre” at implementing reforms over
